name: Unstable (Ryan Kubik)
description:
This is the original beta/jam version of the game Unstable. Play the finished product here: https://www.kongregate.com/games/rmkubik/unstable!

You are teleported to a far away land and have to travel through a variety of different worlds to get back home.

Please leave me any feedback by messaging me on twitter or leaving a comment below. Thanks and enjoy!
